# Copy to .env.local and set the machine that runs `npm run bootstrap` in p2p/.
# Full libp2p multiaddr (WebSocket). Examples:
#   Same computer as browser:  (default if unset — no file needed)
#   LAN demo:                  VITE_BOOTSTRAP_ADDR=/ip4/192.168.1.50/tcp/4012/ws
#   Cloud VM:                  VITE_BOOTSTRAP_ADDR=/ip4/203.0.113.10/tcp/4012/ws
#
#VITE_BOOTSTRAP_ADDR=/ip4/127.0.0.1/tcp/4012/ws
